             <p><lb n="1"/>bhagavā <space unit="character" quantity="1"/> samasabudho <space unit="character" quantity="1"/> sighi <space unit="character" quantity="1"/> vāgāḍhi<add place="above">cā</add>na <space unit="character" quantity="1"/> visāghena <space unit="character" quantity="1"/> saputakena <space unit="character" quantity="1"/> kārito selavaḍhakisa <space unit="character" quantity="1"/> Ā<supplied reason="omitted">sa</supplied>devasa panatu<supplied reason="omitted">ke</supplied>na <lb n="2"/>saminagasa natukena māḍhasa putena <space unit="character" quantity="1"/> nāgabudhinā kato</p>
